<F P=106> [From NIHON KEIZAI SHIMBUN 29 April Morning Edition] </F>
  [Text] Representative Masayoshi Takemura of Sakigake 
[Harbinger] was present at a news conference held on 28 April. 
Regarding Sakigake's formation of a new floor group 
"Sakeigake-Seiun" (tentative name) with the "Group Seiun," 
composed of Dietmen who have left the New Japan Party [JNP], 
