<H3> <TI>   Official Appointments Announced by SLORC </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Official Appointments Announced by SLORC </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Deputy Ministers Appointed </H4>

<F P=102> BK2704143994 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 27 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2704143994 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon Radio Burma </F>
