<H3> <TI>   Party Cell Secretaries Hold Local Conferences </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Party Cell Secretaries Hold Local Conferences </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2804043994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0429 GMT 28 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2804043994 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Conferences of Party Cell Secretaries at Provinces, </F>
Cities, Counties and Complexes" -- KCNA headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, April 28 (KCNA) -- Conferences of party 
cell secretaries took place in provinces, cities, counties and 
complexes after the national conference of party cell 
secretaries was held in Pyongyang. 
  The letter of congratulations sent by the great leader 
President Kim Il-song to the delegates to the national 
conference of party cell secretaries was conveyed to the 
conferences. 
  Reports and speeches were made at the conferences. 
  The conferences laid stress on carrying through the highly 
important tasks laid down in the letter of congratulations sent 
by the great leader to the national conference of party cell 
secretaries and in the letter "Let Us Strengthen the Party 
Cells" sent by the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il to the 
participants in the national short-course of the party cell 
secretaries, in order to make the party cells militant 
organisations which are unfailingly loyal to the party and the 
leader and defend and add lustre to the cause of socialism. 
  The conferences of party cell secretaries fully demonstrated 
the revolutionary faith and will to accomplish the revolutionary 
cause of chuche with credit by enhancing the militant function 
and role of the party cells, the lowest basic organisations of 
the party, and steadily strengthening and developing our party 
into an invincible revolutionary party. 
  The conferences adopted letters of pledge to the great 
leader 
President Kim Il-song and the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

