consultative meeting with South Korean politicians who had 
participated in the joint conference of representatives of 
political parties and public organisations in North and South 
Korea (April 1948) after the liberation of the country and 
showed warm loving care for them. 
  After going round the United Front tower and historical 
relics, the ambassador said he was convinced that the Korean 
people's cause of reunification would certainly be accomplished 
before long. 

