<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Symposium Discusses Kim Il-song's Rural Theses </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Symposium Discusses Kim Il-song's Rural Theses </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2904045794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0440 GMT 29 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2904045794 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 29 (KCNA) -- A national symposium 
on "For the Ultimate Solution of the Rural Question Under the 
Banner of the Socialist Rural Theses", a famous work of the 
great leader President Kim Il-song, was held here on Thursday. 
  The historical letter sent by President Kim Il-song to the 
national agricultural conference on February 24, 1994, gives a 
perfect exposition of the goal and tasks for the final solution 
of the rural question, including the questions of continuously 
pushing ahead with the three revolutions, ideological, technical 
and cultural in the countryside to make the farmers 
revolutionary, assimilate them to the working class and imbue 
them with the socialist idea and with the chuche idea, and of 
improving the technological and cultural standards of the 
agricultural working people to meet the requirements for making 
all the members of the society intellectually-proficient, and 
carrying out the five tasks of electrification, water supply and 
bus service in the rural areas and central heating and gas 
systems in the rural villages to eleminate the distinctions 
between the urban and the rural population in their living 
conditions and complete the industrialisation and modernisation 
of agruculture on a high level, and of converting cooperative 
property into all-people property. 
  The speakers at the symposium said the work which raises the 
final solution of the socialist rural question and the complete 
victory of socialism as immediate practical questions and 
comprehensively indicates tasks for their solution is a great 
programme for the complete victory of socialism. 
  The work is an immortal grand programme which has further 
developed in depth the theory of the working class on the 
socialist rural construction and a true textbook of socialist 
construction which indicates in a unique way the tasks and ways 
for the ultimate solution of the socialist rural question and 
the complete victory of socialism, the speakers stressed. 

</TEXT>

