<F P=102>   SK2804044194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0420 GMT 28 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2804044194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 28 (KCNA) -- "10-point programme of 
the great unity of the whole nation for the reunification of the 
country", a classical work of the great leader President Kim 
Il-song, was carried by the Iranian papers RESALAT and TEHERAN 
TIMES, the Tunisian paper LES ANNONCES and the Nigerian paper 
OBSERVER. 
  Radio Cadena Havana of Cuba and Radio Victoria of Peru 
reported the same work. 
  The Malaysian paper SIN CHEW JIT POH printed a portrait of 
President Kim Il-song and carried the full text of his work "Let 
the North and the South open the way to peace and reunification 
of the country in a united effort". The Russian paper 
ROSSISKAYA PRAVDA and the Ghanaian paper FOCUS carried detailed 
gists of "For the ultimate solution of the rural question under 
the banner of the socialist rural theses", a letter sent by 
President Kim Il-song to a national agricultural conference, and 
the Nepalese paper MAJADUR KISSAN carried the full text of the 
same work. 
  The Mongolian paper ULAN BATOR gave a gist of his work "Let 
us implement the public health law to the letter". 

</TEXT>

