<H3> <TI>   Article Details Pride in Great Leader </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Article Details Pride in Great Leader </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2704104194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1028 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2704104194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 27 (KCNA) -- NODONG SINMUN today 
comes out with an article titled "Our People Proud of Having 
Great Leader". 
  The author of the article says: 
  Our people have a high national pride and honour as they 
have 
the great leader in the person of respected Comrade Kim Il-song 
peerless in their history of thousands of years. 
  As they have the great leader Comrade Kim Il-song and uphold 
his leadership, they become a heroic people who won great 
victories in wars against two formidable imperialist enemies and 
a proud people who have set an example for the century in 
creation and construction. 
  Their pride in having the great leader has been heightened 
as 
they are guided by the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il today. 
  As they have respected Supreme Commander General Kim 
Chong-il, their pride has reached a lofty height and it serves 
as an important ideological and moral source of all their 
victories. 
  Their pride serves as a powerful motive force which enables 
our people to courageously advance along the road of socialism 
under whatever conditions. 
  Our people have victoriously advanced the cause of socialism 
under the banner of the chuche idea, following the guidance of 
the party and the leader. In this course, our people have 
become firmly convinced that the road of socialism led by the 
great leader and the dear leader is the most correct road and 
become proud of building the most advantageous socialism in the 
world. 
  They are successfully building socialism, not wavering under 
the complex situation, because of their high pride of having the 
great leader. 
  Their pride also serves as the source of strength which 
enables them to demonstrate the dignity and honor of the country 
in confrontation with the imperialists. 
  Today our people are famous as a most proud and dignified 
people who resolutely counter any moves of the imperialists and 
firmly defend the cause of Korean-style socialism without the 
slightest vacillation. 
  They are countering the imperialists' anti-socialist 
campaign 
with the conviction that they will win because the great leader 
and the dear leader are leading them and with the unshakable 
will to build Korean-style socialism better under the guidance 
of the party and the leader. 

</TEXT>

