<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Forum Marks Kim Chong-il Work on Trade Unions </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2804045094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0433 GMT 28 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2804045094 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 28 (KCNA) -- A symposium of trade 
union officials was held here Wednesday on the occasion of the 
10th anniversary of the publication of "On further improving the 
work of the trade unions", a famous work of the dear leader 
Comrade Kim Chong-il. 
  Comrade Kim Chong-il in the work says that the trade unions 
are mass political organizations of the working class and 
dependable assistants and defenders of the party and gives 
answers to all the theoretical and practical questions arising 
in the building of the trade unions and their activities. 
  He defines it as the basic duty of the trade unions to 
educate the trade union members and rally them closely around 
the party and powerfully mobilize them in the revolutionary 
struggle and constructive work. 
  He sets it as the most important tasks of the trade unions 
to energetically carry on the ideological, technical and 
cultural revolutions and vigorously rouse the working class and 
trade union members in socialist economic construction. 
  Speakers said that the work of the dear leader was an 
immortal banner which the trade unions must tightly hold in 
accomplishing the revolutionary cause of chuche and a highly 
important guideline which clearly indicates the main 
orientation and target of the trade union activities. 

</TEXT>

