BFN 

  [Text] VNA April 28 -- President Le Duc Anh left Jakarta 
this morning for Bandung and Bali cities, continuing his 
official friendship visit to Indonesia. Before leaving the 
Indonesian capital, President Le Duc Anh expressed his thanks to 
President Suharto and his wife, the Indonesian Government and 
people for their hospitality and expresed his confidence that 
the friendship and cooperation between the two countries would 
