countries. President Le Duc Anh has invited President Suharto 
and his wife to pay an official friendship visit to Vietnam. 
His invitation was accepted with pleasure. President Le Duc 
Anh and his party spent the following day in Bandung and Bali, 
visiting the places of historical and cultural interests in 
those cities in the company of their high-ranking officials as 
the last leg of the president's official friendship visit to 
Indonesia. 

