<F P=100> Vietnam </F>
<H3> <TI>   Prime Minister Meets U.S., Canadian Businessmen </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Prime Minister Meets U.S., Canadian Businessmen </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2904055994 Hanoi VNA in English 1455 GMT 28 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK2904055994 </F>
