<F P=106> ["Statement referring to the amendment of the Serbian </F>
Citizens Council" adopted by the Bosnia-Herzegovina Assembly in 
Sarajevo on 30 March; read by Mariofil Ljubic, deputy chairman 
of the Bosnia-Herzegovina Assembly -- live] 
  [Text] Mr. President, Esteemed Deputies, I would like to 
read the text of a statement: 
  The initiative of the deputies (?launched) at the session 
yesterday that the Assembly of the Republic of 
Bosnia-Herzegovina support the declaration of the congress of 
citizens of Serbian nationality in Bosnia-Herzegovina was 
supported by all deputy caucuses of the parties represented in 
