  [Text] General Shalikashvili, chairman of the Joint Chiefs 
of Staff of the U.S. Armed Forces, arrived this evening in 
Skopje for a one-day visit to The Former Yugoslav Republic of 
Macedonia [FYROM]. Gen. Shalikashvili, who arrived here from 
Sarajevo, is to be received tomorrow by Macedonian President 
Kiro Gligorov and by Stevo Crvenkovski and Vlado Popovski, 
