<F P=102>   AU3103173194 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1600 
GMT 31 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU3103173194 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Bulgarian </F>


<TEXT>
