<H3> <TI>   SDS Confirms Plan on Government Resignation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    SDS Confirms Plan on Government Resignation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU3103173094 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1600 
GMT 31 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU3103173094 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Bulgarian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At a briefing after the extraordinary meeting of 
the Union of Democratic Forces [SDS] National Coordinating 
Council, the SDS confirmed its intention to prompt the 
resignation of the government, which it blames for the financial 
crisis in the country. 
  If the parliament does not adopt an appropriate decision on 
the cabinet's policy, the SDS will propose a new vote of 
no-confidence. The SDS will organize a rally on 5 April at St. 
Aleksandur Nevski Square in Sofia. 

