<H3> <TI>   Cease-Fire Agreement Reached in Bihac Region </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Cease-Fire Agreement Reached in Bihac Region </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Further on Cease-Fire </H4>

<F P=102> AU0104084194 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 0800 GMT 1 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0104084194 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] We have just received a report saying the 
following: An agreement has been reached between Karadzic's 
Serbs and Bosniaks on the cessation of fighting in the Bihac 
region, UNPROFOR [UN Protection Forces] has reported. The 
agreement envisages the separation of forces, buffer zones, 
withdrawal of heavy weapons, the possibility of supervision by 
the UN forces, freedom of movement for international 
humanitarian organizations, and foundation of a joint commission. 

